ecoark holdings inc private company information  bloomberg july    am et software company overview of ecoark holdings inc snapshot people company overview ecoark holdings inc a diversified holding company engages in the development and deployment of business solutions and products to the retail agriculture and food service markets its portfolio of proprietary patented technologies address the waste in operations logistics and supply chain the company through its subsidiary pioneer products llc recycles plastics from reclaimed retailers’ waste streams remanufactures into new consumer products such as plastic trash cans and sells products in the retail market ecoark holdings inc through its subsidiary zest labs inc provides farmers distributors and grocers a freshness management solution focused on reducing food waste ecoark holdings inc a diversified holding company engages in the development and deployment of business solutions and products to the retail agriculture and food service markets its portfolio of proprietary patented technologies address the waste in operations logistics and supply chain the company through its subsidiary pioneer products llc recycles plastics from reclaimed retailers’ waste streams remanufactures into new consumer products such as plastic trash cans and sells products in the retail market ecoark holdings inc through its subsidiary zest labs inc provides farmers distributors and grocers a freshness management solution focused on reducing food waste its flagship product is zest fresh which combines realtime prescriptive analytics with iot productlevel monitoring to enable proactive and intelligent decisionmaking at every step of the fresh food supply chain from field to shelf the company through its subsidiary magnolia solar inc engages in the development production and sale of nanotechnologybased thin film solar cell modules ecoark holdings inc was founded in  and is headquartered in rogers arkansas detailed description  south pinnacle hi