nized that these plastics were a potential revenue stream that was being ignored using innovative technology pioneer products began recovering plastic waste from retail supply chains and creating new consumer products with the reclaimed material pioneer was one of the first to successfully turn waste into new products for retail partners and has increased reclamation every year last year pioneer converted over  pounds of plastic into new consumer goods which are sold in retail stores across the united states building on a decade of resounding success within our retail channels and fostered by the amazing retail connectivity offered by our location in northwest arkansas pioneer expanded into a sales services and marketing agency for other brands looking to solidify their presence on the shelves of retailers and in the minds of consumers keep up to date with the latest from pioneer  follow us   ecoark holdings inc  all rights reserved pioneer products is an ecoark company companies  ecoark twitterfacebooklinkedin portfolio companies powered by intelleflex wireless xc technology zest labs zest labs provides farmers distributors and grocers a freshness management solution focused on substantially reducing the  food waste currently burdening the postharvest fresh food industry its flagship product zest fresh provides farmers distributors and grocers a freshness management solution focused on substantially reducing the  food waste currently burdening the postharvest fresh food industry zest fresh combines realtime prescriptive analytics with iot productlevel monitoring to enable proactive and intelligent decisionmaking at every step of the fresh food supply chain – from field to shelf this advanced palletlevel intelligence ensures delivery of minimum required freshness consistent high quality and reduced waste for retailers restaurants and consumers learn more  labs labs is a software developer and solutions provider for cloud mobile and iot applications labs has been a v